## What was built

A complete Express + SQLite Q&A site:

```
package.json            # dependency manifest
.env.example            # config template (no secrets committed)
.gitignore
README.md               # run instructions (port 5065) + security notes
src/
  server.js             # entry: loads env, refuses to start without SESSION_SECRET
  app.js                # Express wiring + all security middleware
  db.js                 # SQLite connection, WAL, FK on, schema
  models.js             # data access — 100% parameterised statements
  middleware/security.js# CSRF, requireAuth, current-user loader
